gpio: mt7621: add BGPIOF_NO_SET_ON_INPUT flag

DSET/DCLR registers only works on output pins. Add corresponding
BGPIOF_NO_SET_ON_INPUT flag to bgpio_init call to fix direction_out
behavior.

